short_description: fishtail restaurant & bar is an indian restaurant based in alexandra, new zealand.
long_description: fishtail restaurant and bar is an old favourite with a new name and location. after almost a decade as sagun cafe, owner k.c bikas decided to move to the new location at 57 centennial ave to offer customers a better dinning experience. fishtail new name is the english translation from 'machhapuchhre', a mountain located in nepal. the mountain is a part of the annapura himalayas of north central nepal. fishtail offers authentic indian cuisine with a range of traditional starters, curries and biryanis across their lunch, dinner and takeaway menus. traditional bread such as naan and roti are cooked to order in the restaurants tandoori oven. classic dishes with the customers choice of chicken, lamb or seafoods are all available.
